						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up near a pond in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1440, Bahudhānya, Chaitra, ba. 30, Thursday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged and fragmentary. Seems to register the renovation of a tank at Chinagārlapāḍu by [Maṇikyārāvu] Janyāla • • Nāyanigāru.</p>						

